    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 naturally aspirated 4.0L V8, delivering a linear power band and a soaring 8,400 RPM redline. Mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is anchored by the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC), ensuring the MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension geometry perform as intended. Recent preventative maintenance includes throttle valve actuators and a comprehensive fluid service. The hydraulic steering rack offers exceptional feedback, complemented by staggered 19-inch forged alloys. A mechanically sound example of high-revving Bavarian engineering for the discerning purist.",
